snippet.title: Jack Orlando: A Cinematic Adventure gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Jack Orlando: A Cinematic Adventure, Dos PC game produced by Denda Multimedia in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/jack-orlando/12962/
In this video I am playing as a famous private detective, by the name Jack Orlando. This time, I am not working for someone but trying to solve my own case. A nice game with a lot of puzzles where every detail makes a big difference.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:

Murder on the Zinderneuf - https://youtu.be/zeqKMhYS_Ew
Mean Streets - https://youtu.be/WJ4rYt8v--4
